    <div class="flex flex-col justify-between md:max-h-[300px] gap-4">
      <div class="flex flex-col h-full">
        <h6 class="text-sm font-light m-0 text-gray-500">welcome :)</h6>
        <p class="m-0 font-light text-xl">
          My name is <b class="font-bold">Xi Wang (王希)</b>, and I go by <b
            class="font-bold">Joy</b
          >. Born and raised in the beautiful city <a
            href="https://www.google.com/search?q=suzhou&newwindow=1&sca_esv=d3799be6f015f4e8&sca_upv=1&rlz=1C5CHFA_enCA1037CA1039&sxsrf=ADLYWIIvv3hAiwxNEK2XNZ17NuVYoYH2ng%3A1722976248745&ei=-IeyZuSfLeTaptQPnZaGiAk&ved=0ahUKEwjk-4zamuGHAxVkrYkEHR2LAZEQ4dUDCBA&uact=5&oq=suzhou&gs_&sclient=gws-wiz-serp"
            target="_blank"
            class="text-red-500">Suzhou</a
          >, I came to Toronto for <a
            href="https://www.utoronto.ca/"
            target="_blank"
            class="text-red-500">university</a
          > in 2021.
        </p>

        <p class="m-0 font-light text-xl mt-4">
          I am keen on exploring how <b class="font-bold">technology</b> interacts with <b class="font-bold">humans</b> and enhances our well-being. I also care a lot
          about <b class="font-bold">sustainability</b>.
        </p>
        
        <p class="m-0 font-light text-xl mt-4">
          Delighted that you're here! Feel free to explore around.
        </p>
      </div>
